      <td><code>-ef</code></td>
      <td></td>
      <td><code>[[[ &lt;file1&gt; -ef &lt;file2&gt; ]]</code></td>
      </tr>
      </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>If we want to compare joint conditions with <code>and</code>, <code>or</code> and <code>not</code>, we need to use <code>and</code>, <code>or</code> and <code>not</code>.</p>
      <table>
      <thead>
      <tr>
      <th>operation</th>
      <th>command</th>
      <th>example</th>
